g9981PortPm1DayIntervalIndex OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Unsigned32 (1..7) MAX-ACCESS not-accessible STATUS current DESCRIPTION "Performance data interval number. 1 is the most recent previous interval; interval 7 is 24 hours ago. Intervals 2..7 are OPTIONAL.
